result.name: Azores HK

reviews.text:
Very nice Macanese Cuisine restaurant. Their spiced pork bun is incredibly good! Other dishes are good too, but many are sea.food based, so I cannot enjoy those.

The offer some very tasty looking egg tarts, but unfortunately they sell out fast, and I've always been out of luck. Maybe next time.
Service is amazing, waiting time after 7pm is a long time

Disappointing meal. The pork bun was nice, but the curry fried rice was complete contrast. First plate had no pineapples, then requested replacement, this had pineapples but the curry powder was so heavy, we were unable to eat it. Not a nice dining experience if coming for the food. Waitress who served us was nice though.
Good food. Good service.
Pricey yet the quality is just so so.

result.name: YOHO MALL I

reviews.text: A clean, well organised mall with more stores than you can imagine. Well maintained and hygienic restrooms as frequently spaced and the proximity to the MTR is a big plus!

Huge variety! It's great for shopping and dining 👍 they also have a cinema, for entertainment, showing a variety of Western and Asian movies. Pop-up stalls and exhibitions are constantly visiting the mall giving shoppers something interesting to do while walking from shop to shop, or just to celebrate the current events (popular movies, holidays, brands etc.)

Nothing special different from other plaza
It’s crowded. Many mainland people surrounded. 
Although it’s so many restaurant, you need to queue for the restaurant was extremely long.
And the price is not reasonable.
Very disappointed. 
Not recommend.
a grand n morden mall with variaties of dinning places, great to visit...

Many restaurants & cafe, you can find any kind of food & style, this should be the biggest shopping mall at Yuen Long area at moment, very convenient and easy to access, just a min. walk linked with West Rail Yuen Long station.

result.adr_address: 香港元朗元龍街9號形點1期2樓2056號舖
result.formatted_address: 香港元朗元龍街9號形點1期2樓2056號舖
result.name: 亞蘇爾

reviews.text: 比起沙田新城市廣場分店，呢間分店嘅人流明顯無咁虛冚，坐得比較輕鬆自在，而且有室外坐位，夠哂光猛，單係舒適度同好感已經攞咗唔少分數。食物嘅水準係中上，尤其係萄式燒乳豬，皮脆肉滑; 而木糠布甸就既軟滑又層次感分明。基本上各間分店嘅水準郜否會相差大遠，下次想要食嘅話首選嚟呢間，好過喺沙田新城市廣場嗰度迫餐死仲要限時食完。

來到晚飯時間肚子有點餓了
和家人去找東西食 這家未食過所以進去

去到的時候只有幾桌沒有人
看來這家挻受歡迎🤭 幸好不用等位
然後快快下單吧 肚子真的餓了🤣

·鮮橙檸檬/焦糖葡撻 HKD$14/個
鮮橙檸檬味道是第一次食 挻清新的香味
食起上來橙香味在散發著🤭
而焦糖味不會太甜剛剛好的甜度

·葡國雞飯 HKD$128
意想不到地有椰絲鋪在蛋的上面
還有幾片辣肉腸🤣 雞肉不韌挻滑的口感
用這個汁來拌飯是很棒🤭🤭

·葡汁焗青口 HKD$88
第一次看到芝士鋪在青口面上
很多芝士耶😍 興葡汁配合得不錯🤭

·黃金多士伴雪糕 HKD$68
這個味道不錯 多士裡面竟然是吉士醬
另有拖肥醬在旁可以加點甜味🤤
環境舒適，不過有少少嘈，乳豬好食，個辣醬好味，豬扒包就一般，好像西素豬扒包咁，菜就不錯，咖啡撻好有咖啡味，但是個皮比較乾，奶茶也不錯，不過價錢有點小貴！

葡撻個皮幾好,個蛋漿似兩倍甜的普通蛋撻。
意粉幾好, 黑松露好過蜆。
加錢杯飲品好難飲,
跟餐奶茶幾好,較為英式那種. 

環境一般, 茶記+pizza hut 。
樓面好嘈,係咁係旁邊高聲傾偈。

結論: 係元朗有更多更好的選擇。

加12蚊杯芒果蘇打得啖笑，完全係伏！
其它味道一般，份量同價位成反比（食完喫多兩個包先飽）
試過就算，環境唔靜
